Package bankteller.demo1

Class Account

java.lang.Object
bankteller.demo1.Account
Direct Known Subclasses:
Checking, Savings
public abstract class Account extends Object
This abstract class represents an open or closed account held by an account holder with current balance.
Author:
Afsana Rahman, Mini Sinha
